milestones.description: Hansie Cronje and Shaun Pollock's 137-run partnership is SA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Richardson and Jonty Rhodes
This is the highest match aggregate (515) involving teams South Africa & Zimbabwe in ODIs
